snippet.textDisplay: On the last day of exams i started to come down with something, just a tickle in my throat, though now it's developed into really painful coughing and phlegm. Im not necessarily worried i got the Wuhan Corona virus but there's been a lot of kids returning from travel abroad in the last few weeks, and as it is a large school there's always exchange students at any given point in time. The first few confirmed cases in Canada have been recorded recently in a city around two hours away, where the international airport is. A majority of the kids coming back from their end of semester vacations would have come from that airport. U_U
